1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:03,500
[Opening credits roll]

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,200
NARRATOR: In a world where subtitle
formats are incompatible...

3
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:10,500
One filmmaker dared to ask
the hard questions.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,800
ALEX: Why can't my subtitles
just work everywhere?

5
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:18,600
JORDAN: Because the tech industry
decided we needed 47 formats.

6
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:22,100
ALEX: That seems like
a lot of formats.

7
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:25,300
JORDAN: You should see the
image format situation.

8
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:29,500
ALEX: Wait, how many image
formats are there?

9
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:33,200
JORDAN: ConvertICO supports
over 255 conversion tools.

10
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:36,400
ALEX: That's... actually
really impressive.

11
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:40,500
THE BOSS: I need the subtitles
in VTT format by noon!

12
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:44,200
ALEX: But they're in SRT format.
How do I convert them?

13
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:48,000
JORDAN: Have you tried
convertico.com/srt-to-vtt?

14
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:51,800
ALEX: That's... that's a real URL?
That actually exists?

15
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:55,500
JORDAN: It's free, it works
in your browser, and...

16
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:59,200
JORDAN: ...your files never
leave your device.

17
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:02,500
ALEX: You sound like
a privacy policy.

18
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:06,200
JORDAN: I'll take that as a compliment.
Privacy matters.

19
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:09,500
[Alex opens ConvertICO.com
on his laptop]

20
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,300
ALEX: Wait, I can just drag
and drop my file?

21
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:17,000
ALEX: It converted in
two seconds flat!

22
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:20,800
THE BOSS: Excellent work.
Now do it for the other 47 episodes.

23
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:24,500
ALEX: [internal screaming]

24
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:28,200
NARRATOR: And so began the longest
Monday in subtitle history.

25
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:32,000
[To be continued in VTT format]
